                "invention-title": [
                    "Metal diaphragm and preparation method and application thereof",
                    "金属膜片及其制备方法和应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the field of diaphragm compressors, and discloses a metal diaphragm and a preparation method and application thereof. At least one surface layer of the metal diaphragm is a modified layer with a nanocrystallization structure and vacancy clusters. The preparation method of the metal diaphragm comprises the following steps: (1) spraying the surface of a metal substrate diaphragm by using a projectile, wherein the obtained metal substrate diaphragm is provided with a surface nanocrystallization layer; and (2) bombarding the surface nanocrystallization layer of the metal substrate diaphragm by using an ion beam to obtain the metal diaphragm. The metal diaphragm provided by the invention is high in hardness and tensile strength and excellent in wear resistance, and meanwhile, hydrogen can be limited on the surface of the diaphragm and cannot be diffused into the diaphragm, so that the hydrogen embrittlement phenomenon is prevented."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及隔膜压缩机领域，公开了一种金属膜片及其制备方法和应用。所述金属膜片的至少一个表层为具有纳米化结构和空位簇的改性层。所述金属膜片的制备方法包括以下步骤：(1)使用弹丸对金属基材膜片表面进行喷射，得到的金属基材膜片具有表面纳米化层；(2)使用离子束对所述金属基材膜片的表面纳米化层进行轰击，得到所述金属膜片。本发明提供的金属膜片的硬度和拉伸强度高、耐磨性能优良，同时可以使得氢被限制在膜片表面而不能扩散到膜片内部，防止氢脆现象的发生。"
                }
            ]
